::The girl looks at you, silent, but there's a glimmer of hope in her eyes.
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Hello, little one.
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Is there anything I can help with?
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_504096004-->
