::'''Silent Girl:''' ({{MC|f=Miss|m=Sir}}, I've seen a blonde lady before. She was with you.)
::'''Silent Girl:''' (Did... did she leave?)
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} ...Don't worry, she's fine.
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} We'll definitely see her again after the Era Nova.
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_504096009-->
::The girl seems to understand your lip movements. She's silent for a while, looking a little sad.
::'''Silent Girl:''' (I'm sorry, maybe it's my fault...)
