::<!--Custom String Listener: Wait_Option_504096002_28-->
::<!--Custom String Listener: Wait_Option_504096002_28-->
:{{DIcon|Talk}} Can you tell me what happened?
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_504096103-->
::'''Silent Girl:''' (A few days ago, some scary people broke into my house. I saw them whispering, and they said that if that lady didn't disappear, they'd take my eyes.)
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} (Those fiends...!)
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} (They won't spare even a little kid...!)
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} (...Well, but it does fit their character.)
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_504096107-->
::'''Silent Girl:''' (I was scared, but they explained that it's okay, I haven't done anything bad, and that the lady will definitely disappear for me.)
::'''Silent Girl:''' (They seemed... quite troubled. One of them said it was the decision of their leader. That lady... she must have been troubled too...)
::'''Silent Girl:''' (But a purple sprite holding a chest passed by, and it seemed like it was trying to protect me in secret while those people were here. So, I'm fine.)
:;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
:{{DIcon|Talk}} The bad people have already gotten what they deserve.
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_504096111-->
::'''Silent Girl:''' (What they deserve...)
::'''Silent Girl:''' (...Umm, now no one will bully that lady anymore, right?)
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Is there anything else I can help you with?
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_504096114-->
::'''Silent Girl:''' ({{MC|f=Miss|m=Sir}}, if you'd ever see the blonde lady again, can you apologize to her for me?)
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Sure thing.
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_504096118-->
:::'''Silent Girl:''' (Thank you, {{MC|f=miss|m=sir}}.)
::;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Don't worry, this isn't your fault.
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_504096117-->
:::'''Silent Girl:''' (But... if I could protect myself, that lady wouldn't have been bullied. So, please...)
:::<!--Custom String Trigger: TalkSentence_504096118-->
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_504096118-->
:::'''Silent Girl:''' (Thank you, {{MC|f=miss|m=sir}}.)
::;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
:{{DIcon|Exit}} Take care of yourself, and I'll see you next time.
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_504096120-->
